{"tid":1173353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頻表態選總統 韓國瑜：我都是被動的  包括6月1日台北造勢大會","createTime":"2019-05-27T05:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T05:13:56.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a382f9c642041fb3b38dde83b61bac0886ca1f6b","tid":1173353,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"頻表態選總統 韓國瑜：我都是被動的<br />\n<br />\n繼高雄市長韓國瑜日前親口表態「Yes I do」後，也允諾出席6月1日在凱道舉辦的挺韓大會，被外界認定此舉為韓國瑜參選2020的起手勢。儘管話是他自己親口說的，出席事宜也是自己允諾的，但在韓的心中卻認為這些角逐總統大位的言行「都是被動」。<br />\n<br />\n首場總統初選造勢「決戰2020 贏回台灣」將在6月1日於凱到舉行，韓國瑜親口允諾將會參加。韓國瑜決心要參加國民黨總統初選的態勢清楚，日前更親口在接受媒體專訪時親口表示「Yes I do」，因為這句話還被前高雄縣長楊秋興直批「有夠噁心」。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜對於楊秋興的個人想法曾表示予以尊重，但兩人對此事的內心想法顯然不一，因為韓國瑜今(26)日受訪時，被媒體問及「傳出5人小組挺郭？」韓國瑜回應，希望5人小組能夠超然公正，並透過鏡頭再次重申「Yes I do」還強調一切都是被動的。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜重申，如果5人小組來問我Yes I do，如果他們經過評估有特定的參選人自己也沒有意見，「我只說我一切都是被動的，包括6月1日是被動的，包括5人小組來也是被動的。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A0%BB%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E9%81%B8%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%A2%AB%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84-035530968.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C-%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259A%2584-035530968.html&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=e495ff7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A0%BB%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E9%81%B8%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%A2%AB%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84-035530968.html</a>"},{"pid":"baa1fda54e2df0c421fe636bd9066a89213ebe3f","tid":1173353,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=b18cfa0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1d4460f01317adbfbcbfdfbc06f852b1079b6b1d","tid":1173353,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"唔去做戲真係晒咗！"},{"pid":"db04ccfc08bb95a8aa40f219bf01272661d7d94d","tid":1173353,"uid":21411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"嘩！講到黃袍加身咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bda4aea32a166dbf7055b248af068439de6885e","tid":1173353,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d4460f01317adbfbcbfdfbc06f852b1079b6b1d","tid":1173353,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"唔去做戲真係晒咗！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"都要啲觀眾夠on9<br />\n先養到個咁on9既戲子既"},{"pid":"abf71ff04e5a4886894d2d94bafa92a48da202ca","tid":1173353,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"想學人被黃袍加身做王帝"},{"pid":"9ac3a44f31414b99af6c1221657327b1e9431629","tid":1173353,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"如果我係老闆一定請佢做sales head<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}